components:
  schemas:
    tmp0:
      properties:
        error: {type: string}
        id: {type: string}
        join_url: {type: string}
        registrant_id: {type: string}
        start_time: {type: string}
        topic: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp1:
      properties:
        download_url: {type: string}
        file_size: {type: string}
        file_type: {type: string}
        id: {type: string}
        meeting_id: {type: string}
        message: {type: string}
        play_url: {type: string}
        recording_end: {type: string}
        recording_start: {type: string}
        recording_type: {type: string}
        status: {type: string}
      type: object
    tmp2:
      properties:
        agenda: {type: string}
        created_at: {type: string}
        duration: {type: string}
        host_id: {type: string}
        id: {type: string}
        join_url: {type: string}
        password: {type: string}
        start_time: {type: string}
        start_url: {type: string}
        timezone: {type: string}
        topic: {type: string}
        type: {type: string}
        uuid: {type: string}
      type: object
  securitySchemes: {}
info:
  contact: {email: frikky@shuffler.io, name: '@frikkylikeme', url: 'https://twitter.com/frikkylikeme'}
  description: Automated generation of Zoom Zoom
  title: Zoom Zoom
  version: 1.0.0
  x-logo: data:image/png;base64,
openapi: 3.0.2
paths:
  tmp0:
    post:
      description: Add someone to a meeting
      parameters:
      - description: Email address to invite
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Email
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: First name of the registrant
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: First Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Last name of the registrant
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Last Name
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Comments
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Comments
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Meeting ID to add someone to
        example: ''
        in: body
        name: Meeting ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp0'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Zoom Add Meeting Registrant
  tmp1:
    post:
      description: Get the recordings and or chats of a meeting in Zoom
      parameters:
      - description: Meeting ID to get the recording data from
        example: ''
        in: body
        name: Meeting ID
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp1'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Zoom Get Recording & Chats
  tmp2:
    post:
      description: Start a Meeting Zoom
      parameters:
      - description: Email address of the host of the meeting, must be a pro user
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Email
        required: true
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Topic for the meeting
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Topic
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: "Start time in format yyyy-MM-dd\u2019T'HH:mm:ss'Z\u2019"
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Start Time
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Agenda for the meeting
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Agenda
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Optional password for the meeting
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Password
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Start video once host joins the meeting
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Host Starts Video
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      - description: Start video once a participant joins the meeting
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Participants Start Video
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      - description: Are participants able to join the meeting before the host, only
          used for scheduled or recurring meetings
        example: ''
        in: query
        name: Participants Able to Join Before Host
        required: false
        schema: {type: boolean}
      - description: How large the page size for user search should be, used for lookups,
          default 300
        example: ''
        in: body
        name: Page search size
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      - description: Type of approval for joining the meeting, 0 - Automatically Approve,
          1 - Manually Approve, 2 - No Registration Required, default is 2
        example: ''
        in: body
        name: Approval Type
        required: false
        schema: {type: string}
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            application/json:
              schema: {$ref: '#/components/schemas/tmp2'}
          description: Successful request
      summary: Zoom Start Meeting
tags:
- {name: Communication}
